&lt;p&gt;The word &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milonga_(dance)&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;milonga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt; refers both to the dance and dance parties.  If memory serves right, these originated in Argentina and Uruguay.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
